      description : "ALMA-09-042150 - Any AlmaLinux OS 9 world-writable directories must be owned by root, sys, bin, or an application user."
      info        : "If a world-writable directory is not owned by root, sys, bin, or an application user identifier (UID), unauthorized users may be able to modify files created by others.

